}\pard\plain\s0\qj\widctlpar\f0\fs24\sl240\slmult1 \sb240 \fi360 Every case has its own interpretation, which covers economic theory as well as data observation. The first and second case are corner solutions. In both cases {{\field{\*\fldinst{ EQ {\i G}{\i R}{\i T}\\s\\do6({\fs20 {\i m}})}}{\fldrslt }}
